Re: How do Japanese People Type in Japanese?
by keatonatron » Fri 07.10.2009 4:49 pm Animating accurate typing would require twice as many frames, which would require twice as much drawing time, which means you can't get your daily show finished on time.
Searching for models and actors in Tokyo. No experience required!
